text: I deliver here in a sprinter all the time. Always fast, smooth, and friendly. Great job Toyota!!

name: linx finx
text: Great people. Will unloading fast. Mr Calvin very nice, respectful guy and very professional. I'll be happy coming back. Thank you

name: Jason Swingle
text: The first time delivering expesite freight here. It was an easy process.  The guard was helpful in showing where I had to go, gave me a map of the place and assigned a door. The number/letters are big and welll lit above the door. And the receiver was a nice fellow. All in all a good spot to deliver to.
